result.name: Only About Children Melbourne Central

reviews.text: It's been a great experience having my child attending OAC at Melbourne Central. We are so blessed to have such a warm and caring and inspiring team supporting us. Hope we'll get a chance to come back to this big family after we come back from overseas.  All the best!!
Only About Children is wonderful. The carers are all so lovely and the kids absolutely love going every day and I know they are getting the very best care!

Our daughter had been in OAC's nursery for over a year and we love it. The food is fresh, she has had 2 permenant carers in the room the entire time, and they are fantastic.

I feel very happy that so much effort is put into the children's care, education and entertainment.

Imagine your child coming home happy, and requesting to go back to daycare everyday! Absolutely amazing place. Educators and facilities are top notch and the smartphone app is brilliant. Could not recommend this place enough. The central CBD location works well for us, but they have other campuses around melbourne.
